"Fleetwood felt it was too soon to compare those achievements in the aftermath but he will not forget his latest French escapade in a hurry.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1732, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6397128215687352, \"rank\": 0.3446467430552988, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fleetwood\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"those achievements\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"the aftermath\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"a hurry\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is part of me that's disappointed, of course, but at the same time I never dreamt I would be an Olympic medallist,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1812}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medallist\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have not been in the mix that much recently and being back there, playing well and feeling how that felt again, I enjoyed it so much and that's what I will take away \\\"It feels unbelievably special and I know I did not win gold, a very good golfer did, but standing on that podium with a medal was one of the most amazing moments I have had as a golfer.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 2250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mix\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"a very good golfer\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"that podium\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2176}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"the most amazing moments\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"a golfer\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will remember those times for the rest of my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those times\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final day was set up tantalisingly but at one stage it looked like turning into a procession for Jon Rahm.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The final day\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"one stage\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"a procession\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"Jon Rahm\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beginning with a share of the overnight lead, he reached the turn in 31 and held a four-shot lead heading to the 11th tee.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a share\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"the overnight lead\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"the turn\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"a four-shot lead\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"the 11th tee\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that was wiped out in the space of two holes, Fleetwood capitalising on Rahm's consecutive bogeys with successive birdies, and the Spaniard then double-bogeyed the 14th to move out the medal places altogether.\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2594, \"end\": 2603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fleetwood_Town_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9918839592872217, \"rank\": 0.008182420904313077, \"text\": \"Fleetwood\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fleetwood_Town_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fleetwood_Town_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2679, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.8792384602911022, \"rank\": 0.13429905581855833, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the space\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"two holes\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"Rahm's consecutive bogeys\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"successive birdies\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal places\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would not return.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rory McIlroy, who finished fifth on -15, and Victor Perez, a place further up after catching fire down a back nine which required just 29 shots, all of them roared on by his home crowd, threatened the podium but it was Scheffler who ruthlessly seized the initiative.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2780, \"end\": 2792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rory McIlroy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\"}, {\"begin\": 2825, \"end\": 2837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Perez\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.4503475659639418e-11, \"text\": \"Victor Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Perez\"}, {\"begin\": 2999, \"end\": 3008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6054364996024911e-49, \"text\": \"Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"fire\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2877}, {\"ngram\": \"just 29 shots\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"his home crowd\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2987}, {\"ngram\": \"the initiative\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His visible emotion afterwards made it clear that, while golf may not yet be in tennis' league when it comes to theOlympicsrepresenting a 'fifth major', those that play it relish the opportunity to be part of something bigger.\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His visible emotion\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3067}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3109}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis' league\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3142}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'fifth major\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3242}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3253}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am proud of the country, I am proud to be an American,\\\" Scheffler said.\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3335, \"end\": 3344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6054364996024911e-49, \"text\": \"Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got emotional the other night watching the medal ceremony for the women's gymnastics.\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medal ceremony\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3412}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's gymnastics\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I take enormous pride in coming over here and representing my country.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enormous pride\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3464}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you go to a sporting event and hear everyone singing the national anthem, that's something we take enormous pride in and it was very emotional being up there as the flag was being raised.\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sporting event\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3545}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3563}, {\"ngram\": \"the national anthem\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3591}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3609}, {\"ngram\": \"enormous pride\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3632}, {\"ngram\": \"the flag\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's definitely one I will remember for a long time.\\\"\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Typically, Scheffler was on the practice range when news of his victory was confirmed, keeping himself tuned in just in case a play-off was required.\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3775, \"end\": 3784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6054364996024911e-49, \"text\": \"Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pr